{
 "name": "RPlog_Unexpected_Arrivals",
 "title": "Unexpected Arrivals: The Recruitment of Lynae Cassius",
 "summary": "In the rain-soaked Chianar Plaza on Ord Mantell, the exiled former Imperial doctor Lynae Cassius--having handed the New Republic intelligence on the Imperial fleet--crosses paths with the Jedi Ikihsa Enb'Zik and his Horansi wife Snarl, who recognize her and learn of her burned bridges and the standing offer Darth Malign once made her. The quiet conversation is shattered by the arrival of the ex-Imperial Antoine Dareus and the Sith fringer Axel Vichten with armored bodyguard droids, soon joined by the vengeful Cade and Darth Malign himself. Enb'Zik and Snarl try to spirit Lynae to safety, but she chooses to stay and hear out her old comrades, who reveal they serve a breakaway Sith battle group under Malign and offer her command of a modified Interdictor Cruiser. Aboard Lynae's ship, Dareus and Axel make their case for her to join their 'family' as they dock at the black-painted Star Destroyer Predator, where she is welcomed as an honored guest to weigh their offer at her leisure.",
